|YKOThe 'gscore' command (alias 'guildscore') shows one block per learned
guild or innate class recorded on your character:

|BKB* |CKBGuild or class level or Rank, and the maximum where one applies.
|BKB* |CKBWhat your next advance costs - guild XP earned in battle
  (Fighter, Paladin, Cleric of Mitra, Priest, Berserker),
  experience, or carried gold for the Thief guild.
|BKB* |CKBBerserkers also see how much Vex they have to spend.

|YKOYour main learned guild is marked (main). A guild or class your current
equipment restricts is marked (inactive).

